{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>The aim of this post is to provide instructions for setting up a \"Getting Things Done (GTD)\"-style workflow using Notion. It does <em>not</em> cover the workflow itself; it only covers how to setup the necessary views within Notion.</p>\n<!-- end -->\n<p>The target audience is people familiar with GTD that want to try a new tool for implementing it.</p>\n<p>Some context:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>GTD is a methodology or framework for task organization, management, and execution. For details, refer to the excellent summary found <a href=\"https://hamberg.no/gtd/\">here</a>.</li>\n<li>Notion bills itself as an \"all-in-one workspace for your notes, tasks, wikis, and databases\". It's available on web, desktop, and mobile. For details, refer to their website found <a href=\"https://www.notion.so/\">here</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"what-youll-get\"><a href=\"#what-youll-get\" aria-label=\"what youll get permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>What You'll Get</h2>\n<p>Before you continue reading, let's go over the end result:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>View of all tasks</li>\n<li>An inbox of tasks not yet assigned to a context or given a status</li>\n<li>\n<p>Task lists (or boards) filtered by:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Status - <code class=\"language-text\">Up Next</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">In Progress</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Done</code>.</li>\n<li>Context - <code class=\"language-text\">@Computer</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">@Home</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">#Someday</code> etc.</li>\n<li>Project - <code class=\"language-text\">Renovations</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Hawaii Trip</code>, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>A calendar view of tasks</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"requirements\"><a href=\"#requirements\" aria-label=\"requirements permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Requirements</h2>\n<p>You'll need to create an account and log-in to <a href=\"https://www.notion.so/\">Notion</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"steps\"><a href=\"#steps\" aria-label=\"steps permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Steps</h2>\n<h3 id=\"database-creation\"><a href=\"#database-creation\" aria-label=\"database creation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Database Creation</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Create a new page:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Name it <code class=\"language-text\">Tasks</code></li>\n<li>Select the <code class=\"language-text\">Database &gt; Table</code> view</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"custom-block box-shadow\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ed9aea412206106e0209e58d9e15c755/7d158/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 1rem; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 76.29716981132076%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Image 1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ed9aea412206106e0209e58d9e15c755/cf3da/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ed9aea412206106e0209e58d9e15c755/30cce/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_1.jpg 148w,\n/static/ed9aea412206106e0209e58d9e15c755/19047/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_1.jpg 295w,\n/static/ed9aea412206106e0209e58d9e15c755/cf3da/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_1.jpg 590w,\n/static/ed9aea412206106e0209e58d9e15c755/7d158/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_1.jpg 848w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p></div></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Modify the database properties by clicking <code class=\"language-text\">Properties</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"custom-block box-shadow\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/76d46a399ec4f49b5a73f4d33245e8b0/c3fc3/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 1rem; max-width: 380px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 10%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Image 2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/76d46a399ec4f49b5a73f4d33245e8b0/c3fc3/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/76d46a399ec4f49b5a73f4d33245e8b0/55b2e/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_2.jpg 148w,\n/static/76d46a399ec4f49b5a73f4d33245e8b0/91e83/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_2.jpg 295w,\n/static/76d46a399ec4f49b5a73f4d33245e8b0/c3fc3/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_2.jpg 380w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 380px) 100vw, 380px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p></div></div>\n<ol>\n<li>Delete default properties</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add the following properties:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Description - <code class=\"language-text\">Text</code> type</li>\n<li>Context - <code class=\"language-text\">Multi-Select</code> type</li>\n<li>\n<p>Project - <code class=\"language-text\">Multi-Select</code> type</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use <code class=\"language-text\">Select</code> if you want tasks to only belong to a single project</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Status - <code class=\"language-text\">Select</code> type</li>\n<li>Due - <code class=\"language-text\">Date</code> type</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"custom-block box-shadow\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0a991d641adc8395fff9b2b42ec12b67/52d44/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 1rem; max-width: 257px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75.4863813229572%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Image 3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/0a991d641adc8395fff9b2b42ec12b67/52d44/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0a991d641adc8395fff9b2b42ec12b67/99fd5/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_3.jpg 148w,\n/static/0a991d641adc8395fff9b2b42ec12b67/52d44/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_3.jpg 257w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 257px) 100vw, 257px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p></div></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>In the table headers, click <code class=\"language-text\">Status</code> to show the drop-down menu. Then, click <code class=\"language-text\">Configure Options</code> to add default statuses</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Add <code class=\"language-text\">Up Next</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">In Progress</code>, and <code class=\"language-text\">Done</code></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"custom-block box-shadow\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c909ac2e8f588784767e69937e26d18c/67b23/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 1rem; max-width: 217px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 85.71428571428571%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Image 4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c909ac2e8f588784767e69937e26d18c/67b23/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c909ac2e8f588784767e69937e26d18c/3e36f/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_4.jpg 148w,\n/static/c909ac2e8f588784767e69937e26d18c/67b23/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_4.jpg 217w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 217px) 100vw, 217px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p></div></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Now that the primary database is created, you can begin adding tasks into the master task list.\n</p>\n<div class=\"custom-block box-shadow\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/328037112cc62af7151fd9b5c40020a8/8dad9/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 1rem; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 20.959999999999997%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Image 5\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/328037112cc62af7151fd9b5c40020a8/cf3da/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/328037112cc62af7151fd9b5c40020a8/30cce/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_5.jpg 148w,\n/static/328037112cc62af7151fd9b5c40020a8/19047/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_5.jpg 295w,\n/static/328037112cc62af7151fd9b5c40020a8/cf3da/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_5.jpg 590w,\n/static/328037112cc62af7151fd9b5c40020a8/8dad9/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_5.jpg 625w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p></div></div>\n<p><strong>Notes:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>For <code class=\"language-text\">Context</code>, follow the <a href=\"https://hamberg.no/gtd/#contexts\">GTD framework</a> for populating the options. Use contexts such as <code class=\"language-text\">@home</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">@computer</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"view-creation\"><a href=\"#view-creation\" aria-label=\"view creation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>View Creation</h3>\n<p>Now, you can create additional views with specific filtering and sorting for inbox, contexts, projects, calendar, and more.</p>\n<h4 id=\"inbox\"><a href=\"#inbox\" aria-label=\"inbox permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Inbox</h4>\n<p>To create an inbox view:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Click <code class=\"language-text\">Add a View</code> (in the top left)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Name it <code class=\"language-text\">Inbox</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Select <code class=\"language-text\">Table</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"custom-block box-shadow\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ad5c7647f45cc98c8a7cccbf030078e6/1a7eb/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_6.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 1rem; max-width: 273px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 38.82783882783883%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Image 6\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ad5c7647f45cc98c8a7cccbf030078e6/1a7eb/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_6.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ad5c7647f45cc98c8a7cccbf030078e6/c4433/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_6.jpg 148w,\n/static/ad5c7647f45cc98c8a7cccbf030078e6/1a7eb/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_6.jpg 273w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 273px) 100vw, 273px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p></div></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add a filter:</p>\n<div class=\"custom-block box-shadow\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a45e95a76880f4b849b0a70b15e3b2f7/e795f/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 1rem; max-width: 334px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 60.778443113772454%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Image 7\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a45e95a76880f4b849b0a70b15e3b2f7/e795f/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a45e95a76880f4b849b0a70b15e3b2f7/d659b/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_7.jpg 148w,\n/static/a45e95a76880f4b849b0a70b15e3b2f7/a4fa5/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_7.jpg 295w,\n/static/a45e95a76880f4b849b0a70b15e3b2f7/e795f/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_7.jpg 334w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 334px) 100vw, 334px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p></div></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Filter only tasks without a context and that are not done:</p>\n<div class=\"custom-block box-shadow\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4eba5bf836a058dfb8b65d417902ee3c/f1f43/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_8.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 1rem; max-width: 421px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 36.81710213776722%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Image 8\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4eba5bf836a058dfb8b65d417902ee3c/f1f43/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_8.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4eba5bf836a058dfb8b65d417902ee3c/082a5/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_8.jpg 148w,\n/static/4eba5bf836a058dfb8b65d417902ee3c/08aec/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_8.jpg 295w,\n/static/4eba5bf836a058dfb8b65d417902ee3c/f1f43/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_8.jpg 421w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 421px) 100vw, 421px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p></div></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"contexts\"><a href=\"#contexts\" aria-label=\"contexts permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contexts</h4>\n<p>To create a view for a context (e.g. <code class=\"language-text\">@Computer</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">#Someday</code>):</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Click <code class=\"language-text\">Add a View</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Name it <code class=\"language-text\">Context - &lt;CONTEXT_NAME&gt;</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Select <code class=\"language-text\">Table</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add a filter for only tasks matching the context that are not done:</p>\n<div class=\"custom-block box-shadow\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e296019954ddff852f57f6cf877308ae/9cab5/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_9.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 1rem; max-width: 377px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 22.546419098143236%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Image 9\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/e296019954ddff852f57f6cf877308ae/9cab5/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_9.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e296019954ddff852f57f6cf877308ae/bbc0b/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_9.jpg 148w,\n/static/e296019954ddff852f57f6cf877308ae/4fa48/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_9.jpg 295w,\n/static/e296019954ddff852f57f6cf877308ae/9cab5/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_9.jpg 377w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 377px) 100vw, 377px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p></div></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"projects\"><a href=\"#projects\" aria-label=\"projects permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Projects</h4>\n<p>To create a view for a projects:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Click <code class=\"language-text\">Add a View</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Name it <code class=\"language-text\">Project - &lt;PROJECT_NAME&gt;</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Select <code class=\"language-text\">Table</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add a filter for only tasks matching the project that are not done:</p>\n<div class=\"custom-block box-shadow\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/57bbf05e4e4c4ab0f1ddd18d91a119c3/9cab5/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_10.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 1rem; max-width: 377px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 23.872679045092838%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Image 10\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/57bbf05e4e4c4ab0f1ddd18d91a119c3/9cab5/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_10.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/57bbf05e4e4c4ab0f1ddd18d91a119c3/bbc0b/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_10.jpg 148w,\n/static/57bbf05e4e4c4ab0f1ddd18d91a119c3/4fa48/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_10.jpg 295w,\n/static/57bbf05e4e4c4ab0f1ddd18d91a119c3/9cab5/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_10.jpg 377w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 377px) 100vw, 377px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p></div></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"calendar\"><a href=\"#calendar\" aria-label=\"calendar permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Calendar</h4>\n<p>To create a calendar view:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Click <code class=\"language-text\">Add a View</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Name it <code class=\"language-text\">Calendar</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Select <code class=\"language-text\">Calendar</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add a filter for tasks that are not done:</p>\n<div class=\"custom-block box-shadow\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c55c70ceaeb54ee0a814efb1e5241767/13834/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_11.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 1rem; max-width: 275px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 17.454545454545453%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Image 11\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c55c70ceaeb54ee0a814efb1e5241767/13834/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_11.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c55c70ceaeb54ee0a814efb1e5241767/f70bc/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_11.jpg 148w,\n/static/c55c70ceaeb54ee0a814efb1e5241767/13834/2019-03-02-gtd-notion_11.jpg 275w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 275px) 100vw, 275px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p></div></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"additional-views\"><a href=\"#additional-views\" aria-label=\"additional views permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Additional Views</h4>\n<p>To create additional views, follow the same pattern:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Add a new view of a certain type (try <code class=\"language-text\">Board</code> to for Kanban-style)</li>\n<li>Add filters</li>\n<li>Add sorting</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Examples:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Due Soon</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Filter tasks that are not done</li>\n<li>Sort by due date</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"conclusion\"><a href=\"#conclusion\" aria-label=\"conclusion permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Conclusion</h2>\n<p>That's it! If you have any questions, feel free to e-mail me.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 02, 2019","path":"/blog/gtd-notion","title":"Notion + GTD"},"excerpt":"\nThe aim of this post is to provide instructions for setting up a \"Getting Things Done (GTD)\"-style workflow using Notion. It does _not_ cover the workflow itself; it only covers how to setup the necessary views within Notion.\n\n"}},"pageContext":{"prevPost":null,"nextPost":null}}